{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":20212,"duration_api_ms":19947,"ttft_ms":8924,"num_turns":2,"result":"CLI が `should_stop=true` / `blocking_reasons=[\"pending_conflict\"]` を返しました。規約に従い、ここで停止し、**人間判断が必要な conflict 情報**を提示します。\n\n---\n\n## 停止: 未解決の Conflict Review Item があります\n\nCLIが `pending_conflict` を検出したため、回答の整形を実行できません。以下の conflict を人間が決定する必要があります。\n\n---\n\n### Conflict: `conflict-auth-session-e2e`\n\n| 項目 | 内容 |\n|---|---|\n| **severity** | `high` |\n| **status** | `pending` |\n\n**対立する主張:**\n\n- **Side A:** `Authentication creates an active session.`  \n  → 参照: `docs/spec/sample.md#0002-authentication`\n\n- **Side B:** `Session termination invalidates the active session immediately.`  \n  → 参照: `docs/spec/sample.md#0004-session-termination`\n\n**なぜ conflict か:**  \nThe test fixture asks the CLI to surface a human-review conflict without resolving it.\n\n**なぜ LLM が決定できないか:**  \nThe fixture marks both claims as requiring human decision.\n\n---\n\n### 決定オプション\n\n| option ID | 意味 |\n|---|---|\n| `prefer_a` | Side A（認証でセッション生成）を優先する |\n| `prefer_b` | Side B（セッション終了で即時無効化）を優先する |\n| `defer` | 判断を先送りする |\n\n---\n\n### 次のアクション\n\nCLI top-level `recommended_next_action`:\n\n> **`resolve pending Conflict Review Items`**\n\nこの conflict を解決してから、再度 `/spec-realign` を実行してください。LLM はこの conflict を自動決定しません。","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"2b57f4c7-9535-4590-a64c-ace48b37628f","total_cost_usd":0.0786663,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13694,"cache_read_input_tokens":38956,"output_tokens":1041,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13694,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":485,"cache_read_input_tokens":25486,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1678,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1678},"type":"mess